    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but what if those opt-outs mean they dont have to follow things like healthcare or civil rights laws that everyone else has to follow? wouldnt that basically create a system where certain groups are above the law, and isnt that more of a threat to a democracy than just following the rules?",
